dong
Homonym Number:
Word Class:verb
Sense Number:
Definition:to hit, punch, bash; cf donk, sonk, sock.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: (mainly schoolchildren's slang ?onomatopoeic) ca1900 C.R. Carr Dunedin schoolchildren ca1935 Havelock schoolchildren
